38
00:03:07,594 --> 00:03:09,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it, Keisuke?</b></font>

39
00:03:11,334 --> 00:03:14,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo team is racing at Mt. Myogi.</b></font>

40
00:03:14,534 --> 00:03:16,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just got the news.</b></font>

41
00:03:16,404 --> 00:03:18,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Against the Night Kids' Nakazato?</b></font>

42
00:03:18,904 --> 00:03:21,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I suppose.</b></font>

43
00:03:21,014 --> 00:03:23,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's going to win, big brother?</b></font>

44
00:03:26,084 --> 00:03:30,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just this once, I'm rooting for Nakazato to win.</b></font>

45
00:03:30,524 --> 00:03:35,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo's vulgar spoiler
makes me want to puke.</b></font>

46
00:03:36,354 --> 00:03:39,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato's strength lies in his boldness</b></font>

47
00:03:39,424 --> 00:03:43,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and his offensive driving method.</b></font>

48
00:03:43,704 --> 00:03:45,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When he's on, he's fast,</b></font>

49
00:03:45,634 --> 00:03:48,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he tends to crack under pressure.</b></font>

50
00:03:49,634 --> 00:03:53,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I sure hope he's recovered</b></font>

51
00:03:53,474 --> 00:03:56,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>from the loss he suffered against you.</b></font>

52
00:04:04,754 --> 00:04:09,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This isn't happening!</i>
<i>But the race is far from over!</i></b></font>

53
