<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I don't stop them...</i></b></font>

54
00:04:14,764 --> 00:04:17,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...who will?!</i></b></font>

55
00:04:36,114 --> 00:04:37,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn it!</b></font>

56
00:04:39,024 --> 00:04:42,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We get your team sticker, as promised.</b></font>

57
00:04:46,864 --> 00:04:50,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In no time, my Evo IV's spoiler will be covered</b></font>

58
00:04:50,094 --> 00:04:55,074
