the pathetic cry of a loser.</b></font>

62
00:05:05,084 --> 00:05:08,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Let's go, Seiji.
--Yeah.</b></font>

63
00:05:08,514 --> 00:05:10,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way...</b></font>

64
00:05:10,084 --> 00:05:13,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...from now on, you pull
over whenever you see</b></font>

65
00:05:13,524 --> 00:05:16,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a car with the Emperor sticker on it.</b></font>

66
00:05:34,014 --> 00:05:39,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takeshi... I still can't believe he was
