<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Seriously?</b></font>

69
00:05:48,024 --> 00:05:51,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all anyone's talking about this morning.</b></font>

70
00:05:51,694 --> 00:05:56,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato's R32 crashed into a wall
and suffered severe damage.</b></font>

71
00:05:56,034 --> 00:05:58,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's tragic.</b></font>

72
