for the Night Kids lately.</b></font>

73
00:06:00,234 --> 00:06:03,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel bad for them.</b></font>

74
00:06:03,034 --> 00:06:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard that the Lan-Evo squad is planning</b></font>

75
00:06:05,844 --> 00:06:09,174
