<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do we do if they come here?!</b></font>

78
00:06:15,254 --> 00:06:18,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have no choice but to face them.</b></font>

79
00:06:18,254 --> 00:06:21,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're Akina's team, so if they challenge us,</b></font>

80
00:06:21,354 --> 00:06:24,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no intention of running away.</b></font>

81
00:06:24,264 --> 00:06:26,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've already switched my S13's tires</b></font>

82
00:06:26,724 --> 00:06:28,734
