83
00:06:28,734 --> 00:06:31,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I informed the team members already.</b></font>

84
00:06:31,034 --> 00:06:33,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much.</b></font>

85
00:06:33,704 --> 00:06:35,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi.</b></font>

86
00:06:35,674 --> 00:06:40,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They may specifically challenge
you to a downhill battle,</b></font>

87
00:06:40,004 --> 00:06:42,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you can just ignore them.</b></font>

88
00:06:43,274 --> 00:06:46,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your undefeated streak is our pride.</b></font>

89
00:06:46,914 --> 00:06:50,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd hate to ruin it against a Lan-Evo.</b></font>

90
00:06:50,114 --> 00:06:54,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not officially a Speed Star, either.</b></font>

91
00:06:54,294 --> 00:06:57,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want you to keep winning, too.</b></font>

92
00:06:57,364 --> 00:06:59,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo is no joke.</b></font>

93
00:06:59,694 --> 00:07:03,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like racing against a WRC rally car.</b></font>

94
00:07:03,734 --> 00:07:07,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its light body is equipped
with turbo and 4WD.</b></font>

95
00:07:07,834 --> 00:07:10,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It has no real weaknesses.</b></font>

96
00:07:10,504 --> 00:07:14,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car shouldn't be allowed on any pass.</b></font>

97
00:07:14,244 --> 00:07:17,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hate to...</b></font>

98
00:07:17,484 --> 00:07:19,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hate to avoid a race.</b></font>

99
00:07:19,514 --> 00:07:23,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to race them, too.</b></font>

100
00:07:26,754 --> 00:07:30,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, you sound like a true racer now!</b></font>

101
00:07:30,994 --> 00:07:34,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're my true friend! I love it!</b></font>

102
00:07:34,064 --> 00:07:36,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm positive you'll win!</b></font>

103
00:07:36,934 --> 00:07:40,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Lan-Evo is going down!</b></font>

104
00:07:40,334 --> 00:07:43,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that wise?</b></font>

105
00:07:43,174 --> 00:07:47,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right now, his chance of winning is...</b></font>

106
00:07:47,004 --> 00:07:48,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...zero percent.</b></font>

107
00:07:48,744 --> 00:07:51,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

108
00:07:52,114 --> 00:07:55,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Upgrading the Eight-Six?</b></font>

109
00:07:55,054 --> 00:07:58,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That came out of nowhere, Yuichi.</b></font>

110
00:07:58,284 --> 00:08:01,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure it's crossed your mind.</b></font>

111
00:08:01,724 --> 00:08:05,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since Takumi is evolving into a fine racer,</b></font>

112
00:08:05,064 --> 00:08:07,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like it's about time to upgrade</b></font>

113
00:08:07,394 --> 00:08:11,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the Eight-Six's capabilities to match his needs.</b></font>

114
00:08:13,564 --> 00:08:18,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't get me wrong.
I'm not telling you what to do.</b></font>

115
00:08:18,304 --> 00:08:21,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just want to know your plans.</b></font>

116
00:08:21,244 --> 00:08:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess this engine is getting old,</b></font>

117
00:08:26,244 --> 00:08:29,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and it's about time to overhaul it.</b></font>

118
00:08:29,384 --> 00:08:30,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

119
00:08:30,824 --> 00:08:33,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Actually...</b></font>

120
00:08:33,254 --> 00:08:34,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I have one already.</b></font>

121
00:08:34,754 --> 00:08:36,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

122
00:08:36,254 --> 00:08:37,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that true?</b></font>

123
00:08:37,994 --> 00:08:41,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I happened to get an incredible thing</b></font>

124
00:08:41,094 --> 00:08:43,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>from an unlikely source.</b></font>

125
00:08:43,764 --> 00:08:46,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An incredible thing?</b></font>

126
00:08:46,334 --> 00:08:50,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, I'll show it to you. Get in the car.</b></font>

127
00:08:50,744 --> 00:08:52,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll get chills.</b></font>

128
00:08:59,284 --> 00:09:01,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Suzuki Motors"</b></font>

129
00:09:06,224 --> 00:09:10,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is incredible! This is gold!</b></font>

130
00:09:10,224 --> 00:09:12,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got chills, didn't you?</b></font>

131
00:09:12,394 --> 00:09:15,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More than that. It blew me away!</b></font>

132
00:09:15,734 --> 00:09:19,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did you manage to get this?</b></font>

133
00:09:19,004 --> 00:09:22,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm already psyched about the
idea of this in the Eight-Six.</b></font>

134
00:09:22,474 --> 00:09:24,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me, too.</b></font>

135
00:09:24,044 --> 00:09:26,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I haven't felt this excited in a while.</b></font>

136
00:09:26,674 --> 00:09:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's almost too good for Takumi, isn't it?</b></font>

137
00:09:30,014 --> 00:09:33,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When are you putting it in?</b></font>

138
00:09:34,254 --> 00:09:36,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll see.</b></font>

139
00:09:36,014 --> 00:09:40,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A better engine won't
automatically make the car better.</b></font>

140
00:09:40,654 --> 00:09:45,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll need to adjust many things
and fine-tune the "footwork."</b></font>

141
00:09:45,024 --> 00:09:49,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With the right balance,
it'll be an incredible machine.</b></font>

142
00:09:49,034 --> 00:09:53,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll test it myself and come up
with the best configuration.</b></font>

143
00:09:53,204 --> 00:09:56,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll need your help then, Masashi.</b></font>

144
00:09:56,034 --> 00:09:59,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No problem, but you're so darn stubborn.</b></font>

145
00:09:59,404 --> 00:10:02,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You never compromise.</b></font>

146
00:10:02,914 --> 00:10:05,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is like the old days.</b></font>

147
00:10:05,684 --> 00:10:07,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But there is one more thing</b></font>

148
00:10:07,784 --> 00:10:11,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi hasn't accomplished in that car.</b></font>

149
00:10:13,124 --> 00:10:15,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is that?</b></font>

150
00:10:16,694 --> 00:10:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing, really.</b></font>

151
00:10:18,024 --> 00:10:20,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop teasing and tell us.</b></font>

152
00:10:20,794 --> 00:10:24,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll tell you, but you have to promise me</b></font>

153
00:10:24,204 --> 00:10:26,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>not to tell Takumi about this.</b></font>

154
00:10:28,234 --> 00:10:30,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We won't tell him.</b></font>

155
00:10:30,304 --> 00:10:33,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then I'll tell you.</b></font>

156
00:10:33,404 --> 00:10:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That one thing is...</b></font>

157
00:10:40,244 --> 00:10:42,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...losing a race.</b></font>

158
00:10:44,924 --> 00:10:46,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

159
00:10:46,584 --> 00:10:50,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi has tried so hard
to remain undefeated.</b></font>

160
00:10:50,624 --> 00:10:53,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what I don't like.</b></font>

161
00:10:53,094 --> 00:10:54,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As long as he's winning,</b></font>

162
00:10:54,834 --> 00:10:58,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he won't have a true
appreciation for this upgrade.</b></font>

163
00:10:58,964 --> 00:11:03,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He needs to push the car's
capabilities to the very limit</b></font>

164
00:11:03,404 --> 00:11:06,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and find out that it's still
not good enough to win.</b></font>

165
00:11:06,404 --> 00:11:09,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a lesson to be learned</b></font>

166
00:11:09,244 --> 00:11:11,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>in that humiliation.</b></font>

167
00:11:15,014 --> 00:11:17,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until he loses...</b></font>

168
00:11:17,854 --> 00:11:20,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I can't upgrade the Eight-Six.</b></font>

169
00:11:42,314 --> 00:11:43,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this rate,</b></font>

170
00:11:43,974 --> 00:11:47,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the side of the spoiler
will be covered in no time.</b></font>

171
00:11:47,454 --> 00:11:51,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's kind of fun if I think of it as a game.</b></font>

172
00:11:51,324 --> 00:11:54,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I wanna race more capable racers.</b></font>

173
00:11:54,994 --> 00:11:58,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where's our next target, Kyoichi?</b></font>

174
00:11:58,764 --> 00:12:02,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tomorrow night, we'll head to Akina.</b></font>

175
00:12:02,394 --> 00:12:06,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six... how boring!</b></font>

176
00:12:08,234 --> 00:12:11,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't mind doing it myself, Seiji.</b></font>

177
00:12:11,074 --> 00:12:12,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

178
00:12:12,344 --> 00:12:15,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi will race him? Why?</b></font>

179
00:12:15,574 --> 00:12:17,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

180
00:12:17,344 --> 00:12:19,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our ultimate target...</b></font>

181
00:12:19,384 --> 00:12:23,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is Ryosuke Takahashi of the Akagi Red Suns.</b></font>

182
00:12:23,184 --> 00:12:27,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But before that, we'll defeat Akina's Eight-Six.</b></font>

183
00:12:29,024 --> 00:12:31,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I went to see the course yesterday.</b></font>

184
00:12:31,064 --> 00:12:34,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The slope is severe.</b></font>

185
00:12:34,024 --> 00:12:36,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My Evo III is lighter and better suited for it.</b></font>

186
00:12:36,234 --> 00:12:40,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You kidding me? Let me take him, Kyoichi.</b></font>

187
00:12:40,634 --> 00:12:44,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter where I race, I won't lose to anyone.</b></font>

188
00:12:44,874 --> 00:12:51,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is only one car that
my Evo IV can't beat, Kyoichi.</b></font>

189
00:12:51,144 --> 00:12:53,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's your Evo III.</b></font>

190
00:12:56,084 --> 00:13:00,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Team Emperor's ace is not
needed against an Eight-Six.</b></font>

191
00:13:00,994 --> 00:13:02,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll do it.</b></font>

192
00:13:14,774 --> 00:13:17,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's this?</b></font>

193
00:13:17,774 --> 00:13:19,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Do you know that Natsuki Mogi</b></font>

194
00:13:19,674 --> 00:13:24,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is dating an older man
in a Mercedes for money?"</b></font>

195
00:13:26,384 --> 00:13:27,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"...Natsuki Mogi..."</b></font>

196
00:13:27,884 --> 00:13:29,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"...dating..."</b></font>

197
00:13:32,384 --> 00:13:34,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

198
00:13:36,124 --> 00:13:39,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Ready to go?
--Yeah.</b></font>

199
00:13:39,894 --> 00:13:41,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you have there?</b></font>

200
00:13:41,634 --> 00:13:43,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's nothing.</b></font>

201
00:13:47,534 --> 00:13:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi?</b></font>

202
00:13:49,874 --> 00:13:52,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This car magazine I bought recently</b></font>

203
00:13:52,544 --> 00:13:55,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has a feature article on the Evo IV,</b></font>

204
00:13:55,374 --> 00:13:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so maybe you should read it.</b></font>

205
00:13:57,614 --> 00:14:01,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You may be battling against one.</b></font>

206
00:14:01,154 --> 00:14:03,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, thanks.</b></font>

207
00:14:03,484 --> 00:14:06,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why? I'm sure it'll be very helpful.</b></font>

208
00:14:06,924 --> 00:14:10,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I probably wouldn't know what to do</b></font>

209
00:14:10,224 --> 00:14:13,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with the knowledge after reading the article.</b></font>

210
00:14:13,824 --> 00:14:16,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can I drive the Eight-Six faster?</b></font>

211
00:14:16,834 --> 00:14:19,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all I think about.</b></font>

212
00:14:19,504 --> 00:14:22,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't matter which car I go up against.</b></font>

213
00:14:26,174 --> 00:14:31,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Haven't you ever considered getting
a more powerful engine or something?</b></font>

214
00:14:35,054 --> 00:14:37,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not really.</b></font>

215
00:14:37,014 --> 00:14:42,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seriously? I'm dying for more
power for my Eight-Five!</b></font>

216
00:14:47,894 --> 00:14:50,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A more powerful engine...</b></font>

217
00:15:07,484 --> 00:15:09,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no clue.</b></font>

218
00:15:19,494 --> 00:15:24,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Takumi!
--What's going on, Iketani?</b></font>

219
00:15:24,334 --> 00:15:27,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're coming to Akina.</b></font>

220
00:15:27,404 --> 00:15:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tonight.</b></font>

221
00:15:34,714 --> 00:15:37,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here comes the Lan-Evo squad!</b></font>

222
00:15:43,214 --> 00:15:46,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This will be an incredible battle.</b></font>

223
00:16:01,804 --> 00:16:05,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come! The Lan-Evo squad!</b></font>

224
00:16:07,974 --> 00:16:10,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That white Evo IV in front must be the one</b></font>

225
00:16:10,544 --> 00:16:13,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that defeated Nakazato in Myogi.</b></font>

226
00:16:13,484 --> 00:16:17,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rumor has it that he's ridiculously fast.</b></font>

227
00:16:28,764 --> 00:16:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew it! The guys I met at Akina Lake!</b></font>

228
00:16:32,334 --> 00:16:34,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you're the Speed Stars.</b></font>

229
00:16:34,534 --> 00:16:38,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Sudo, the leader of Team Emperor.</b></font>

230
00:16:38,674 --> 00:16:43,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure you already know
that we have only one demand.</b></font>

231
00:16:43,074 --> 00:16:45,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A downhill race against your Eight-Six.</b></font>

232
00:16:45,844 --> 00:16:48,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all.</b></font>

233
00:16:48,354 --> 00:16:52,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll accept all your demands.</b></font>

234
00:16:52,124 --> 00:16:56,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Any number of races, of any type,
under any conditions.</b></font>

235
00:16:56,224 --> 00:17:00,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if you fail to win even one race,</b></font>

236
00:17:00,794 --> 00:17:04,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we'll take your team sticker. Understood?</b></font>

237
00:17:04,034 --> 00:17:05,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our sticker?</b></font>

238
00:17:05,404 --> 00:17:08,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What are they gonna do with it?
--No idea.</b></font>

239
00:17:08,404 --> 00:17:11,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--It's okay, right?
--We accept.</b></font>

240
00:17:11,644 --> 00:17:15,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then let's get right to the race.</b></font>

241
00:17:15,474 --> 00:17:18,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't have much time.</b></font>

242
00:17:18,144 --> 00:17:21,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The first race is the main downhill race.</b></font>

243
00:17:21,814 --> 00:17:23,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have your Eight-Six ready.</b></font>

244
00:17:23,684 --> 00:17:26,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's racing for you?</b></font>

245
00:17:26,654 --> 00:17:29,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I am, and I drive an Evo IV.</b></font>

246
00:17:36,164 --> 00:17:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani, they said they were
ready for more than one race...</b></font>

247
00:17:40,364 --> 00:17:43,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...so who's racing after Takumi?</b></font>

248
00:17:43,704 --> 00:17:47,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Takumi loses, I'll race next.</b></font>

249
00:17:47,344 --> 00:17:52,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he can beat Takumi, I sure
won't be able to beat him...</b></font>

250
00:17:52,044 --> 00:17:56,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but we can't accept defeat without a fight.</b></font>

251
00:17:56,454 --> 00:17:59,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then I'll race after you.</b></font>

252
00:18:00,684 --> 00:18:04,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've been relying on Takumi too much lately.</b></font>

253
00:18:04,464 --> 00:18:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's show him that we're capable, too!</b></font>

254
00:18:07,864 --> 00:18:09,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah!</b></font>

255
00:18:12,964 --> 00:18:15,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm counting on you, our leadoff man!</b></font>

256
00:18:18,244 --> 00:18:20,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go get him!</b></font>

257
00:18:24,484 --> 00:18:27,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here comes Fujiwara Tofu Shop!</b></font>

258
00:18:27,984 --> 00:18:30,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six vs. the Evo IV!</b></font>

259
00:18:38,824 --> 00:18:42,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good luck, Gunma's downhill hero!</b></font>

260
00:18:45,164 --> 00:18:48,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't take this lightly, Seiji.</b></font>

261
00:18:48,104 --> 00:18:51,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go with "Simulation 3."</b></font>

262
00:18:51,034 --> 00:18:53,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Are you serious?</b></font>

263
00:18:53,704 --> 00:18:57,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Simulation 3" against an Eight-Six?</b></font>

264
00:18:57,114 --> 00:18:59,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

265
00:18:59,384 --> 00:19:03,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can tell. I felt his energy.</i></b></font>

266
00:19:03,514 --> 00:19:07,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This Eight-Six is capable. He's not a fake.</i></b></font>

267
00:19:07,354 --> 00:19:10,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He has something that</i>
<i>made him defeat Ryosuke.</i></b></font>

268
00:19:10,454 --> 00:19:14,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Until we know what it is,</i>
<i>we can't let our guard down.</i></b></font>

269
00:19:14,324 --> 00:19:15,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll count down.</b></font>

270
00:19:15,794 --> 00:19:19,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, no need for that.</b></font>

271
00:19:19,134 --> 00:19:23,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a race, not a time trial.</b></font>

272
00:19:23,134 --> 00:19:27,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The one with less engine power
can start whenever he likes.</b></font>

273
00:19:27,644 --> 00:19:30,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The other starts accordingly.</b></font>

274
00:19:30,974 --> 00:19:32,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll start late,</b></font>

275
00:19:32,714 --> 00:19:35,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but that's our handicap for
having more horsepower.</b></font>

276
00:19:35,984 --> 00:19:39,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We call it the "Handicap Method."</b></font>

277
00:19:39,484 --> 00:19:41,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you say?</b></font>

278
00:19:41,494 --> 00:19:44,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it's okay with you, Takumi.</b></font>

279
00:19:48,494 --> 00:19:52,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I saw him once by Akina Lake.</i></b></font>

280
00:19:52,204 --> 00:19:56,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It never occurred to me</i>
<i>that a young kid like him</i></b></font>

281
00:19:56,274 --> 00:19:58,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>was the driver of Akina's Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

282
00:19:59,874 --> 00:20:02,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kyoichi has developed three strategies to win</i></b></font>

283
00:20:02,244 --> 00:20:05,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>on an opponent's course.</i></b></font>

284
00:20:05,014 --> 00:20:09,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Simulation 3" is only used</i>
<i>against the toughest opponents,</i></b></font>

285
00:20:09,914 --> 00:20:13,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>so why use it against this Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

286
00:20:13,524 --> 00:20:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't get it.</i></b></font>

287
00:20:21,534 --> 00:20:23,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi zoomed out!</b></font>

288
00:20:23,064 --> 00:20:25,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go, Takumi!</b></font>

289
00:20:37,814 --> 00:20:40,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't show you how great the Evo IV is...</b></font>

290
00:20:40,584 --> 00:20:42,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but how incredible I am!</b></font>

291
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Furikaereba itsudatte</i></b></font>

292
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kawaranu kimi no egao ga atta</i></b></font>

293
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Arukitsukare tachidomaru hi mo</i></b></font>

294
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Chiisa na yorokobi no hi mo</i></b></font>

295
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kono ryoute ni kakaekirenai</i></b></font>

296
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai wo oshiete kureta</i></b></font>

297
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Atatakaku</i></b></font>

298
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sotto yasashiku yomigaeru kaze wa</i></b></font>

299
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ima hitori sora wo</i></b></font>

300
00:22:23,554 --> 00:22:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mitsumeteru boku ni hohoendeiru</i></b></font>

301
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mada ano hi no mama no</i></b></font>

302
00:22:38,704 --> 00:22:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mabushisa de te wo futteiru</i></b></font>

303
00:22:51,384 --> 00:22:57,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kimi wa everlasting memory</i></b></font>

304
00:23:04,424 --> 00:23:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The race has begun!</i></b></font>

305
00:23:06,364 --> 00:23:09,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does Seiji understand the reason</i>
<i>for using "Simulation 3"?</i></b></font>

306
00:23:09,994 --> 00:23:12,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: Second Stage...</i></b></font>

307
00:23:12,234 --> 00:23:13,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Premonition of Defeat."</i></b></font>

